<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Investment Term Sheet</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; line-height: 1.6; margin: 40px; }
        .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .parties { border: 2px solid #000; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .section { margin: 25px 0; }
        .clause { margin: 15px 0; }
        .fill-in { border-bottom: 1px solid #000; min-width: 150px; }
        h1 { font-size: 18px; text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase; }
        h2 { font-size: 16px; margin-top: 30px; color: #333; }
        h3 { font-size: 14px; margin-top: 20px; }
        table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 15px 0; }
        th, td { border: 1px solid #000; padding: 8px; text-align: left; }
        th { background-color: #f0f0f0; font-weight: bold; }
        .key-terms { border: 2px solid #000; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; background-color: #f9f9f9; }
        .important { background-color: #ffffcc; padding: 10px; border-left: 4px solid #ff0000; margin: 15px 0; }
        .checkbox { display: inline-block; width: 15px; height: 15px; border: 1px solid #000; margin-right: 5px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>INVESTMENT TERM SHEET</h1>
        <h2>Series <span class="fill-in">___</span> Preferred Stock Financing</h2>
        <p><strong>Company:</strong> <span class="fill-in">_________________________</span></p>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> <span class="fill-in">_________________</span></p>
        <p><strong>CONFIDENTIAL - FOR DISCUSSION PURPOSES ONLY</strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="parties">
        <p><strong>COMPANY:</strong></p>
        <p>Name: <span class="fill-in">_________________________</span></p>
        <p>CIN: <span class="fill-in">_________________________</span></p>
        <p>Address: <span class="fill-in">____________________</span></p>
        <p><span class="fill-in">_____________________________</span></p>
        <p>("Company")</p>

        <p><strong>INVESTOR(S):</strong></p>
        <p>Lead Investor: <span class="fill-in">_________________________</span></p>
        <p>Address: <span class="fill-in">____________________</span></p>
        <p><span class="fill-in">_____________________________</span></p>
        <p>Other Investors: <span class="fill-in">_________________________</span></p>
        <p>("Investors")</p>
    </div>

    <div class="key-terms">
        <h2>KEY INVESTMENT TERMS</h2>
        
        <table>
            <tr>
                <th style="width: 30%;">Term</th>
                <th style="width: 70%;">Details</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><strong>Investment Amount</strong></td>
                <td>₹<span class="fill-in">_________</span> crores</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><strong>Pre-Money Valuation</strong></td>
                <td>₹<span class="fill-in">_________</span> crores</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><strong>Post-Money Valuation</strong></td>
                <td>₹<span class="fill-in">_________</span> crores</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><strong>Investor Ownership</strong></td>
                <td><span class="fill-in">____</span>% of Company on fully diluted basis</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><strong>Security Type</strong></td>
                <td>Series <span class="fill-in">___</span> Compulsorily Convertible Preference Shares (CCPS)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><strong>Price per Share</strong></td>
                <td>₹<span class="fill-in">_____</span> per share</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>1. SECURITIES AND RIGHTS</h2>
        
        <div class="clause">
            <h3>1.1 Preferred Stock Rights</h3>
            <p>The Series <span class="fill-in">___</span> Preferred Stock shall have the following rights:</p>
            
            <div class="important">
                <p><strong>LIQUIDATION PREFERENCE:</strong></p>
                <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> <strong>Non-participating:</strong> <span class="fill-in">___</span>x liquidation preference</p>
                <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> <strong>Participating:</strong> <span class="fill-in">___</span>x liquidation preference plus participation</p>
                <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> <strong>Cap on participation:</strong> <span class="fill-in">___</span>x total return</p>
                
                <p><strong>DIVIDEND RIGHTS:</strong></p>
                <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Cumulative dividend at <span class="fill-in">___</span>% per annum</p>
                <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Non-cumulative dividend</p>
                <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Participating in common stock dividends</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h3>1.2 Conversion Rights</h3>
            <p><strong>Mandatory Conversion:</strong></p>
            <p>• IPO with valuation ≥ ₹<span class="fill-in">_____</span> crores and proceeds ≥ ₹<span class="fill-in">_____</span> crores</p>
            <p>• Majority investor consent</p>
            
            <p><strong>Optional Conversion:</strong></p>
            <p>• At any time at holder's option</p>
            <p>• Initially 1:1 ratio, subject to anti-dilution adjustments</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h3>1.3 Anti-Dilution Protection</h3>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> <strong>Full Ratchet:</strong> Complete protection against down rounds</p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> <strong>Weighted Average Broad-Based:</strong> Standard market protection</p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> <strong>Weighted Average Narrow-Based:</strong> Limited protection</p>
            
            <p><strong>Exceptions:</strong> Employee stock option grants, conversions, stock splits, and other standard exceptions</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>2. BOARD OF DIRECTORS</h2>
        
        <div class="clause">
            <h3>2.1 Board Composition</h3>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <th>Board Size</th>
                    <td><span class="fill-in">___</span> directors total</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Investor Directors</th>
                    <td><span class="fill-in">___</span> directors appointed by Investors</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Common Directors</th>
                    <td><span class="fill-in">___</span> directors appointed by Common shareholders</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Independent Directors</th>
                    <td><span class="fill-in">___</span> independent directors (mutual consent)</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h3>2.2 Board Matters Requiring Investor Director Approval</h3>
            <p>• CEO hiring/firing and compensation</p>
            <p>• Annual budget and business plan</p>
            <p>• Major strategic decisions and partnerships</p>
            <p>• Subsequent fundraising rounds</p>
            <p>• M&A transactions</p>
            <p>• Stock option pool creation/expansion</p>
            <p>• Debt financing above ₹<span class="fill-in">_____</span> lakhs</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>3. INVESTOR RIGHTS</h2>
        
        <div class="clause">
            <h3>3.1 Information Rights</h3>
            <p><strong>Regular Reporting:</strong></p>
            <p>• Monthly financial statements within <span class="fill-in">___</span> days</p>
            <p>• Quarterly board meetings with detailed reports</p>
            <p>• Annual audited financial statements</p>
            <p>• Annual budget and business plan</p>
            <p>• Material contracts and legal proceedings updates</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h3>3.2 Inspection Rights</h3>
            <p>• Reasonable access to company books and records</p>
            <p>• Right to inspect facilities with reasonable notice</p>
            <p>• Access to management for periodic updates</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h3>3.3 Preemptive Rights</h3>
            <p>• Right to maintain pro-rata ownership in future financing rounds</p>
            <p>• <span class="fill-in">___</span> days notice of proposed equity issuance</p>
            <p>• Right to purchase up to <span class="fill-in">___</span>% of new shares</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>4. TRANSFER RESTRICTIONS</h2>
        
        <div class="clause">
            <h3>4.1 Tag-Along Rights</h3>
            <p>If Founders sell shares to third party, Investors have right to sell same percentage of their holdings on same terms and conditions.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h3>4.2 Drag-Along Rights</h3>
            <p>If holders of majority of shares approve sale to third party, all shareholders must sell their shares on same terms.</p>
            <p><strong>Trigger:</strong> Approval by holders of <span class="fill-in">___</span>% of shares</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h3>4.3 Right of First Refusal (ROFR)</h3>
            <p>Company and then Investors have right of first refusal on any proposed transfer of shares by Founders/employees.</p>
            <p><strong>Process:</strong> <span class="fill-in">___</span> days notice, <span class="fill-in">___</span> days to exercise</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>5. FOUNDER AND EMPLOYEE PROVISIONS</h2>
        
        <div class="clause">
            <h3>5.1 Founder Vesting</h3>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <th>Vesting Period</th>
                    <td><span class="fill-in">___</span> years</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Cliff Period</th>
                    <td><span class="fill-in">___</span> year</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Acceleration</th>
                    <td>
                        <span class="checkbox">☐</span> Single trigger (change of control)<br>
                        <span class="checkbox">☐</span> Double trigger (change of control + termination)
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h3>5.2 Employee Stock Option Pool</h3>
            <p><strong>Pool Size:</strong> <span class="fill-in">___</span>% of post-money shares reserved for employees</p>
            <p><strong>Expansion:</strong> Board approval required for pool expansion</p>
            <p><strong>Administration:</strong> Board-appointed compensation committee</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h3>5.3 Key Person Insurance</h3>
            <p><strong>Coverage Amount:</strong> ₹<span class="fill-in">_____</span> crores per key founder</p>
            <p><strong>Beneficiary:</strong> Company</p>
            <p><strong>Key Persons:</strong> <span class="fill-in">_________________________</span></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>6. PROTECTIVE PROVISIONS</h2>
        
        <div class="clause">
            <h3>6.1 Investor Consent Required</h3>
            <p>The following actions require approval of holders of majority of Preferred Stock:</p>
            
            <div class="important">
                <p>• Liquidation, dissolution, or winding up of Company</p>
                <p>• Amendment to Articles of Association affecting Investor rights</p>
                <p>• Issuance of equity securities (except under employee plans)</p>
                <p>• Payment of dividends on Common Stock</p>
                <p>• Redemption or repurchase of shares</p>
                <p>• Sale of assets >₹<span class="fill-in">_____</span> lakhs</p>
                <p>• Related party transactions >₹<span class="fill-in">_____</span> lakhs</p>
                <p>• Change in business or entry into new line of business</p>
                <p>• Incurring debt >₹<span class="fill-in">_____</span> lakhs</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>7. CONDITIONS PRECEDENT</h2>
        
        <div class="clause">
            <h3>7.1 Conditions to Investment</h3>
            <p>Investment is subject to completion of the following:</p>
            
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Satisfactory completion of due diligence</p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Execution of definitive investment agreements</p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Board and shareholder approvals</p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Legal opinions on key matters</p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Key employee agreements executed</p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Regulatory approvals (if required)</p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Insurance policies in place</p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> IP assignments and protection</p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> Other: <span class="fill-in">_________________________</span></p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h3>7.2 Timeline</h3>
            <p><strong>Due Diligence Completion:</strong> <span class="fill-in">___</span> weeks from signing</p>
            <p><strong>Definitive Agreements:</strong> <span class="fill-in">___</span> weeks from term sheet execution</p>
            <p><strong>Closing:</strong> <span class="fill-in">___</span> weeks from definitive agreements</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>8. USE OF FUNDS</h2>
        
        <div class="clause">
            <h3>8.1 Allocation of Investment Proceeds</h3>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <th style="width: 60%;">Use Category</th>
                    <th style="width: 20%;">Amount (₹)</th>
                    <th style="width: 20%;">Percentage</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Product Development & Technology</td>
                    <td><span class="fill-in">_______</span></td>
                    <td><span class="fill-in">___</span>%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Sales & Marketing</td>
                    <td><span class="fill-in">_______</span></td>
                    <td><span class="fill-in">___</span>%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Team Expansion</td>
                    <td><span class="fill-in">_______</span></td>
                    <td><span class="fill-in">___</span>%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Working Capital</td>
                    <td><span class="fill-in">_______</span></td>
                    <td><span class="fill-in">___</span>%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Other</td>
                    <td><span class="fill-in">_______</span></td>
                    <td><span class="fill-in">___</span>%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Total</strong></td>
                    <td><strong><span class="fill-in">_______</span></strong></td>
                    <td><strong>100%</strong></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>9. OTHER TERMS</h2>
        
        <div class="clause">
            <h3>9.1 Registration Rights</h3>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> <strong>Demand Rights:</strong> <span class="fill-in">___</span> demand registrations</p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> <strong>Piggyback Rights:</strong> Right to participate in Company registrations</p>
            <p><span class="checkbox">☐</span> <strong>S-3 Rights:</strong> Short-form registration rights</p>
            <p><strong>Registration Expenses:</strong> Borne by Company (except underwriting discounts)</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h3>9.2 Representations and Warranties</h3>
            <p>Standard representations and warranties from Company regarding:</p>
            <p>• Corporate organization and authority</p>
            <p>• Financial statements accuracy</p>
            <p>• Legal compliance and litigation</p>
            <p>• Intellectual property ownership</p>
            <p>• Material contracts and commitments</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clause">
            <h3>9.3 Legal Costs</h3>
            <p><strong>Company's Legal Costs:</strong> Company bears own costs</p>
            <p><strong>Investors' Legal Costs:</strong> Company to reimburse up to ₹<span class="fill-in">_____</span> lakhs</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 40px; border-top: 2px solid #000; padding-top: 20px;">
        <h2>SIGNATURES</h2>
        <p><strong>This term sheet is non-binding except for confidentiality, exclusivity, and legal cost provisions.</strong></p>
        
        <table width="100%">
            <tr>
                <td width="50%">
                    <p><strong>COMPANY:</strong></p>
                    <p>[Company Name]</p>
                    <br><br>
                    <p>By: _________________________</p>
                    <p>Name: _______________________</p>
                    <p>Title: CEO</p>
                    <p>Date: ______________________</p>
                </td>
                <td width="50%">
                    <p><strong>LEAD INVESTOR:</strong></p>
                    <p>[Investor Name]</p>
                    <br><br>
                    <p>By: _________________________</p>
                    <p>Name: _______________________</p>
                    <p>Title: _____________________</p>
                    <p>Date: ______________________</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <div class="important">
            <p><strong>BINDING PROVISIONS:</strong></p>
            <p>• <strong>Confidentiality:</strong> 2 years from signing</p>
            <p>• <strong>Exclusivity:</strong> <span class="fill-in">___</span> days (Company shall not solicit other investors)</p>
            <p>• <strong>Legal Costs:</strong> As specified above</p>
            <p>• <strong>Governing Law:</strong> Indian law, Delhi jurisdiction</p>
        </div>
        
        <br>
        <p><strong>IMPORTANT NOTICE:</strong></p>
        <p>This term sheet is for discussion purposes only and does not constitute a binding agreement except for specific provisions noted above. Definitive agreements will contain additional terms and conditions.</p>
        
        <p><strong>Template Source:</strong> The Indian Startup - P5 Legal Stack<br>
        <strong>Version:</strong> 2.0 | <strong>Last Updated:</strong> December 2024<br>
        <strong>Jurisdiction:</strong> India | <strong>Review Required:</strong> Legal and financial advisors essential</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>